 and even cannibalism throughout Europe.","jurisdictionLevel":2},{"id":1705192,"age":33,"year":"1328","julianDay":2206102,"title":"First War of Scottish Independence","description":"The First War of Scottish Independence began after England invaded Scotland in 1296. The Treaty of Edinburgh was signed in 1328 which declared peace between the two kingdoms and brought the war to an end.","jurisdictionLevel":2}],"lifeSummary":"Sir Thomas De Reyney was born in 1295, in Frome, Somerset, England as the son of Reyney and Mrs. Reyney. He had at least 2 daughters with Mrs. Thomas De Reyney. He died in 1328, in Rowde, Wiltshire, England, at the age of 33."},"et":{"1295–1328":"1295–1328","1295–Female":"1295–Surnud","1320–Female":"1320–Surnud","1325–Female":"1325–Surnud","–1295":"–1295","–Female":"Surnud","1315":"1315","1325":"1325","1320":"1320","before 1295":"enne 1295","after 1295":"pärast 1295","1295":"1295","1328":"1328","1317":"1317","Somerset, England":"Somerset, England","Rowde, Wiltshire, England":"Rowde, Wiltshire, England","England":"England","Boscawen, Cornwall":"Boscawen, Merrimack, New Hampshire, Ameerika Ühendriigid","Frome, Somerset, England":"Frome, Somerset, England"},"fi":{"1295–1328":"1295–1328","1295–Female":"1295–Kuollut","1320–Female":"1320–Kuollut","1325–Female":"1325–Kuollut","–1295":"–1295","–Female":"Kuollut","1315":"1315","1325":"1325","1320":"1320","before 1295":"ennen vuotta 1295","after 1295":"1295 jälkeen","1295":"1295","1328":"1328","1317":"1317","Somerset, England":"Somerset, England","Rowde, Wiltshire, England":"Rowde, Wiltshire, England","England":"England","Boscawen, Cornwall":"Boscawen, Merrimack, New Hampshire, Yhdysvallat","Frome, Somerset, England":"Frome, Somerset, England"},"fr":{"1295–1328":"1295–1328","1295–Female":"1295–Décédée","1320–Female":"1320–Décédée","1325–Female":"1325–Décédée","–1295":"–1295","–Female":"Décédée","1315":"1315","1325":"1325","1320":"1320","before 1295":"avant 1295","after 1295":"après 1295","1295":"1295","1328